## Proprietary Elements

The following files are **NOT open source** and remain the exclusive property of RELEASE255:

- KiCad source files
- PCB routing & layout
- Gerber files
- 3D model of the actual PCB

**These files are not included in this repository and may not be reproduced without written permission.**

